      "A friend messaged me on my 10,000th day alive. She had calculated it in advance, set a reminder, and on the actual day sent me: 'You have been here for 10,000 days today. That is a lot of days.' I had to sit with that for a moment. I knew I was 27. I did not know I was 10,000 days old. Those two facts describe the same thing and they feel entirely different.",
