    slug: "do-love-calculators-actually-work-science-and-fun",
    title: "Do Online Love Calculators Actually Work? The Science and Fun Behind Compatibility Tests",
    excerpt: "Love calculators are everywhere — but what are they actually measuring? Here's an honest look at the psychology, the fun, and what these tools tell you that a real relationship test never could.",
    date: "March 31, 2026",
    updatedDate: "April 11, 2026",
    author: "Sneha Patel",
